source.name: Formal Enforcement Actions Fiscal Year 2011
source.description: The annual data tables contained in this document provide summary statistics on the civil enforcement activities of the United States Trustee Program.  These tables summarize data for Fiscal Year 2005 through Fiscal Year 2011 (October 1, 2004 through September 30, 2011).  This report covers formal actions.  Formal actions include all motions, complaints, and objections filed by Program personnel with the bankruptcy court seeking some type of relief.
